short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension enhances Keap for FixYourFunnel users.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Login to this Chrome Extension to get enhanced abilities inside of Infusionsoft, including:
* Call and Text directly from
  * My Day
  * Quick Search Results
  * Opportunity Lists
  * Contact Records
  * Contact Search Results
  * Company Records
* Listen to FixYourFunnel call recordings directly in the contact record.
* View live text chat archives in easy to read format.
